{"tid":1134608,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［整理］女生虐打貓","createTime":"2019-05-01T21:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T14:37:03.000Z","uid":138740,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"60df4c064a1a922b77c2b829b35eed0a1ddb97c9","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:14:29.000Z","msg":"最初嘅post <br />\nUST 內地女生虐打同住人嘅貓<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1132346\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1132346</a><br />\n事件簡述：發生地點同涉事人都喺中國<br />\n打貓個女仔係合租人 貓主人係屋主<br />\n 屋主當初有講明屋內廳嘅範圍有裝cam 係為咗得閒睇下隻貓。同埋問過女仔介唔介意有養貓，個女仔表示自己好鍾意貓，可以合租好好彩。<br />\n但當時喺海外旅遊嘅屋主通過cam發現個女仔打貓 <br />\n佢嘗試聯絡個女仔 最初失聯同唔肯道歉 所以貓主迫於無奈利用網絡想得到合理嘅回應 同埋叫咗朋友接走隻貓去睇醫生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2hWYkr5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2hWYkr5.jpg&h=3a99241d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8if666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8if666.jpg&h=1389da21&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n貓主本身係唔想搞大件事 但個女仔唔合作<br />\n<br />\n下面有證據片段<br />\n以下係原文嘅重點部分<br />\n4月27日在我去泰國旅遊不在家期間，合租人董怡萱在凌晨1到2點，一個多小時在各種追趕、毆打、欺凌取樂我的貓！非常凶狠足力的踢踹、毆打幾十次我那沒有一點反抗能力的小貓，甚至提著它的尾巴不放下來聽著我的貓慘叫取樂三分半鐘之長！還把貓關在貓砂盆里10多分鐘有餘，將活動門抵住電視櫃又拿靠枕塞住縫隙讓貓咪無法出來無法呼吸，她就站在一旁聽著貓的慘叫笑！把貓按在沙發上掐住脖子，一邊自己發出興奮的令人毛骨悚然的尖叫！這一系列令人發指的虐貓行為被我在客廳一角的攝像頭全程記錄下來。以下僅為幾秒的gif截圖已如此令人發指，貓全程哀嚎但都沒有一點防衛攻擊動作，受到的傷害可想而知。<br />\n目前董怡萱對此事毫無歉意，事發時我立即電聯她不接甚至按掉繼續虐貓，理智溝通她也表示就是要打貓，報警隨便的挑釁態度。在相關部門調解後依舊毫無愧疚，從未真誠道歉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8P3ccF8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8P3ccF8.gif&h=c698c198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ok0Var8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fok0Var8.gif&h=3d658604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Dy0myP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Dy0myP.gif&h=d29b1d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0u3ccFw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0u3ccFw.gif&h=ab2df709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5Feq0G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5Feq0G.gif&h=92eff3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VaJLN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VaJLN.jpg&h=19727ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sD61QqN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsD61QqN.jpg&h=216d347c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABt0mx3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABt0mx3.jpg&h=3fdfcdbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9vueS3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9vueS3.jpg&h=39caef88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmMAUS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmMAUS4.jpg&h=947a4ec0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4fc565b01711973b5d9446fc50340b54812ddc7","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:15:23.000Z","msg":"西伯利亞J巴打同宮崎喵巴打提供嘅format<br />\nSend to:<br />\npao@ust.hk [UST PR]<br />\nmedia@ust.hk [UST PR]<br />\nssci@ust.hk [理學院]<br />\n<br />\ncc:<br />\nalumni@ust.hk<br />\nocpe@ust.hk<br />\ncareercenter@ust.hk [比UST學生搵工既 career center]<br />\nssvivien@ust.hk [Science UG Program contact person]<br />\ntinako@ust.hk [Science school student advising]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDear sir/madam,<br />\n<br />\nAn intolerable incident induced by HKUST UG student named 董怡萱 has came under attention of the public. I am hereby writing to express the urge of handling the issue in order to withhold the reputation of HKUST, its fellow students and their alumni.<br />\n<br />\nThe incident was unfolded when several photos were posted on a renown Hong Kong online discussion forum - LIHKG, with the heading「UST 內地女生虐打同住人嘅貓」, link as below,<br />\n [<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1132346](https://lih.kg/1132346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1132346](https://lih.kg/1132346</a>) <br />\n<br />\nFrom those photos, evidently Miss Dong was attacking a cat maliciously. Also, form the snapshots of Miss Dong's communication with her flatmate, she has not shown a single bit of regret about her brutal actions. Meanwhile, a negative impression about UST student is spreading due to her misconduct and I believe the administration should be well aware of the subsequent adverse effects.<br />\n<br />\nWith the wishes to make HKUST a better place for education, I genuinely hope that HKUST would take follow-up actions with regards to the incident.<br />\n<br />\nBest regards,<br />\n你個名"},{"pid":"c3ece908b5a058bcb0cefcd0dd45b1b346109c10","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:16:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocwEPmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocwEPmC.jpg&h=7829c1f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouTjPmD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouTjPmD.jpg&h=1cc5c3f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z73LKUY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz73LKUY.png&h=c1624130&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kZnM8i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kZnM8i.jpg&h=c1ecd1be&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n校方同騰訊嘅回應 <br />\n實習已經被暫停"},{"pid":"403f339a2f685ed1f4d762aa5a3e1799d1acbfbd","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qvvY4Vm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqvvY4Vm.jpg&h=dbf52dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人透露了已經唔係第一次虐貓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CeJ4f2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCeJ4f2d.jpg&h=b1c25a92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n先前隻貓都試過受傷 不過無確實證據"},{"pid":"95d8eac1dbfcddec2504f2ba8c5a52d826d91fe3","tid":1134608,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:24:35.000Z","msg":"中國人，正常啦<br />\n唔係沒事兒就他只是個孩子架啦"},{"pid":"ab80a130ee2d5d6f64b40b306c4d163fc3e02a10","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fY8zDgb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfY8zDgb.jpg&h=9c8beb22&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h1iPr9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh1iPr9w.jpg&h=2b2b2175&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VbnQbBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbnQbBc.jpg&h=e799be80&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n貓主多次upload相關片段 但都係被消失<br />\n <br />\n上半段<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1245318904/4367104168236697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F1245318904%2F4367104168236697&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmRIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=48969f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/1245318904/4367104168236697</a><br />\n下半段<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1245318904/4367099303032524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2F1245318904%2F4367099303032524&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmRIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=5ae7c73a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/1245318904/4367099303032524</a><br />\n唔知點Post片上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我依排有好多嘢做 唔可以再捕住消息"},{"pid":"815378533d911d85fbf62542c9122377c1abc8ca","tid":1134608,"uid":202014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:28:28.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ef40892a4e74a4ace7c0700a70281238cfc190","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:29:31.000Z","msg":"上一個post入面啲資料可能有搬漏 睇到嘅幫幫手搬過嚟 <br />\n蘋果嘅報導 大家唔洗去蘋果搵嚟睇<br />\n喺到睇啦 喺到睇唔洗註冊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYY0ySJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYY0ySJ.jpg&h=a5466318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報-<strong>【宿友舉報】香港科大內地女生虐貓？ 騰訊：如核實將終止實習</strong><br />\n內地女網民今日在微博舉報，指在香港科技大學就讀、現於騰訊TEG戰略發展中心實習的董姓女宿友涉嫌虐貓，趁她27日到泰國旅遊時，於凌晨在家中對其貓施虐，並留言說：「一個多小時在各種追趕、毆打、欺凌取樂我的貓！」校方稱正向涉事的女生了解；騰訊公司則對該女網民表示非常重視事件，若事件屬實，將終止該女生的實習工作，並為其提供心理輔導。<br />\n<br />\n該女網民@vseacuvuenm在微博發佈長文和閉路電視影片，指來自北京的合租女宿友董女對其貓咪毆打幾十次，甚至拿着尾巴取樂，還把貓關在貓砂盆內，再將活動門靠向電視櫃，再用枕頭塞住縫隙，令貓無法走出和呼吸，她就站在一旁聽着貓慘叫。<br />\n雙方在微信對話時，董女指貓咪在其床上瀨尿，她才出手「懲戒」。女網民形容董女「對此事毫無歉意」，還向她表示：「就是要打貓，報警隨便的挑釁態度」。她決定將事件公開，並向香港科技大學和騰訊公司舉報，希望給予董女應有的裁決。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者晚上嘗試聯絡女網民，以及董姓女宿友，暫時沒有回覆。"},{"pid":"2c60781d182847b1a5e34585cad750809b1c908f","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vg93wF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVg93wF2.png&h=c297710f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話：正義點都會嚟"},{"pid":"237a9212b7cb76d2027e31db2c308da0d4e65d46","tid":1134608,"uid":78304,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:43:37.000Z","msg":"中國北姑呀<br />\n唔撚係內地,唔撚係女生"},{"pid":"0e2159c087a546d9b509a256ad89bf049a693581","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:16:07.000Z","msg":"有人睇到有新消息嘅 麻煩post喺到<br />\n原先個post太亂"},{"pid":"424348f81be3fc6b6a7f678a688fd9913123b6cb","tid":1134608,"uid":113215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0e9789025b04092ea8e4d0f59433ac8e51ad9f","tid":1134608,"uid":12015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"仲以為有新消息"},{"pid":"92bf44553efa065de5461e9b18b14f9df2858457","tid":1134608,"uid":80814,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:30:17.000Z","msg":"虐貓條蝗婦個老豆係幹部<br />\n仲要去騰訊實習<br />\n果然嚟得香港讀書嘅支那蝗都唔係普通人"},{"pid":"3ba4c0479674ca05646839b901b90b77485a90dd","tid":1134608,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84462a4d3e838b32cce343fe5794f691a1fbca4","tid":1134608,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b4d9348b63691947411bb83e069fcc63e883fcc5","tid":1134608,"uid":162073,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"我只係睇到女事主對波好大應該幾好玩"},{"pid":"a9031f739366849b2c0e0d754369938bbf07225a","tid":1134608,"uid":137480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c60781d182847b1a5e34585cad750809b1c908f","tid":1134608,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T21:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vg93wF2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVg93wF2.png&h=c297710f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話：正義點都會嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"沒錯支那人冇一個係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e1f41028a295ffc60d6b